		<title>什么是外汇交易？它是如何运作的？</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/trading-strategies/what-is-forex-trading-how-does-it-work</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
